Set MAVEN_HOME in Environment variables as "C:\maven-3.0.5\apache-maven-3.0.5"

Copy hadoop-core-1.0.4 to C:\maven-3.0.5\apache-maven-3.0.5\lib.

Modify pom.xml to include the location of above jar file.

Inclue above entry in Path variable as %MAVEN_HOME%\bin;

C:\cygwin\usr\local\hadoop\src\examples\wordcount>mvn compile

C:\cygwin\usr\local\hadoop\src\examples\wordcount>mvn package

